## How to Deploy to Production

Install pre-requisites:

```
$ brew install redis
$ cd /path/to/charted.co
$ npm install
$ cd /path/to/charted
$ npm install
```

Update Charted to the latest version:

```
$ cd /path/to/charted
$ bin/build --prod
$ cp -r out /path/to/charted.co/charted
```

Verify:

```
$ redis-server
$ heroku local web
```

Deploy:

```
$ git push heroku master
```

## Plugins

If you want display additional information on the homepage,
Charted has a basic system of plugins. Just create two files,
`header.html` and `footer.html` in the plugins directory and
then run the build step with `--plugins`:

$ bin/build --prod --plugin=/path/to/charted.co/plugins

